+#: package/contents/ui/ChangeWalletPassword.qml:32
+#, kde-format
+msgid "Change Wallet Password?"
+msgstr "更改密码库密码？"
+
+#: package/contents/ui/ChangeWalletPassword.qml:42
+#, kde-format
+msgctxt "@info"
+msgid "Now that you have changed your login password, you may also want to change the password on your default KWallet to match it."
+msgstr "既然您已经更改了登录密码，您也需要更改默认密码库的密码以匹配它。"
+
+#: package/contents/ui/ChangeWalletPassword.qml:47
+#, kde-format
+msgid "What is KWallet?"
+msgstr "密码库是什么"
+
+#: package/contents/ui/ChangeWalletPassword.qml:57
+#, kde-format
+msgid "KWallet is a password manager that stores your passwords for wireless networks and other encrypted resources. It is locked with its own password which differs from your login password. If the two passwords match, it can be unlocked at login automatically so you don't have to enter the KWallet password yourself."
+msgstr "密码库是一个密码管理器，用于存储您的无线网络和其他加密资源的密码。它使用自己的密码锁定，这与您的登录密码不同。如果两个密码匹配，则可以在登录时自动解锁，因此您不必自己输入密码库密码"
+
+#: package/contents/ui/ChangeWalletPassword.qml:73
+#, kde-format
+msgid "Change Wallet Password"
+msgstr "更改密码库密码"
+
+#: package/contents/ui/ChangeWalletPassword.qml:82
+#, kde-format
+msgid "Leave Unchanged"
+msgstr "保持不变"
